name: Another World (itch) (baekily)
description:
Another World is a platformer puzzle game. Players have the power to travel to another world after they have collected enough energy from the map. After accessing a new world, players will find the hidden map that will allow them to locate the next step in the journey. However, they only have 10 seconds!

Move -- A/D

Jump -- Space

I would be grateful if you could leave your feedback on:

https://forms.office.com/e/mGZSKEcerC
